title: George Osborne – 2020 Comments on Jeremy Corbyn’s Suspension from the Labour Party
author: admin
summary: The comments made by George Osborne, the former Chancellor of the Exchequer, on 30 October 2020.
content: Without irony, Len McCluskey says suspending Corbyn could cost Labour the next election – when it was his support for Corbyn that cost Labour the last two elections
